{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Environmental Financial Activism"}},"allSitePage":{"nodes":[{"context":{"numPages":3,"currentPage":1}}]},"allMarkdownRemark":{"totalCount":11,"edges":[{"node":{"excerpt":"The world’s full of pithy headlines: “How to stop procrastinating.” “Learn to code in 15 minutes.” “7 Emails you should send every week.” “How to Learn any Language in 3 Months.” They’re needy. They overpromise. And they underdeliver. They always do. This is post about learning Dutch the slow way…","fields":{"slug":"how-to-learn-dutch-the-slow-way"},"frontmatter":{"date":"02 <span> Jun </span>","title":"Learning Dutch the Slow Way","description":"I am not a polyglot and I do not have a natural predisposition to language learning. In language classroom settings, I'm a middling student. However, over the past year, I have managed to teach myself A2 to B1 level Dutch without attending in-person classes. Here's how.","tags":["education","dutch"],"cover":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"tracedSVG":"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='62'%20height='62'%20viewBox='0%200%2062%2062'%20preserveAspectRatio='none'%3e%3cpath%20d='M27%207c-6%201-10%202-13%201-4%200-5%200-9%204l-5%204v19l1%2018%205%202c13%204%2023%202%2032-8%202-3%205-5%206-5%206%200%2012-9%2013-17%200-5%200-6-2-7-3-2-8-2-13%200-2%200-2%200-1-3l1-7c0-3-1-4-4-4L27%207'%20fill='%23d3d3d3'%20fill-rule='evenodd'/%3e%3c/svg%3e","aspectRatio":1,"src":"/static/d651d2fe26d1aca36eda4ad4f6a52269/c5f1a/clogs-klompen.jpg","srcSet":"/static/d651d2fe26d1aca36eda4ad4f6a52269/76bb0/clogs-klompen.jpg 81w,\n/static/d651d2fe26d1aca36eda4ad4f6a52269/587d4/clogs-klompen.jpg 163w,\n/static/d651d2fe26d1aca36eda4ad4f6a52269/c5f1a/clogs-klompen.jpg 325w,\n/static/d651d2fe26d1aca36eda4ad4f6a52269/ae913/clogs-klompen.jpg 488w,\n/static/d651d2fe26d1aca36eda4ad4f6a52269/0a3fd/clogs-klompen.jpg 500w","srcWebp":"/static/d651d2fe26d1aca36eda4ad4f6a52269/986c5/clogs-klompen.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/d65